  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Constructing Server Components**\n\nI\'m currently focused on building the `server.ts` file. This involves setting up an Express API server with integration for both development (Vite) and production (static files). My next step is to create the `/api/generate` endpoint, which will utilize the `@google/genai` SDK and the `gemini-3.5-` model. This is where I\'ll implement the core generation logic.\n\n\n**Designing Story Context**\n\nI\'m now designing the story context and focusing on ensuring that the pre-written chapters provide a strong foundation for continuation. I am hardcoding initial chapters based on the previous 5 parts, ensuring a seamless flow for the user\'s next prompt to flash. This involves carefully selecting and integrating the most intense parts for optimal storytelling. Then I\'m working to write the continuation of the story from Part 5. Finally, I will add the continuation into the applet as well.\n\n\n**Crafting Narrative Continuation**\n\nI am now crafting a continuation based on recent events. I\'m focusing on the aftermath: the physical and emotional states of both characters post-climax. I\'m building on their immediate vulnerabilities and establishing Song Yu\'s intentions and Han Li\'s humiliation and internal struggle. The chapter title, \"\347\254\254XXX\347\253\240\357\274\232\350\215\257\346\225\210\346\270\220\351\200\200\357\274\214\344\273\231\345\255\220\347\232\204\344\275\231\346\270\251\344\270\216\350\252\223\350\250\200,\" sets the stage for a period of revelation and uneasy alliance. I am establishing tension in both the physical and emotional aftermath.\n\n\n**Exploring Narrative Consequences**\n\nI\'m now contemplating the disciples, and the potential threat they pose. The blackmail angle, and the secret relationship dynamic, really interests me. Han Li\'s predicament \342\200\223 his helplessness intertwined with pleasure \342\200\223 makes for a compelling conflict. This could significantly impact the narrative going forward.\n\n\n**Implementing User Interface**\n\nI\'m now building the user interface for chapter continuation. I\'ve added a text area labeled \"\347\273\255\345\206\231\344\270\213\344\270\200\346\255\245\345\211\247\346\203\205...\" for user prompts. I\'ve included shortcut buttons for common plot directions, offering options like Han Li recovering power or Song Yu making more demands, which will send prompts. Clicking \"AI \347\273\255\345\206\231\344\270\213\344\270\200\347\253\240\" calls the server-side Gemini API. This generates the next chapter and appends it to the story, with local storage ensuring persistence.\n\n\n**Initializing Gemini API**\n\nI am now initializing the Gemini API within `server.ts`. I\'ve added the necessary import for `@google/genai` and configured the client with the API key and a custom user agent. I am also working on creating the `POST /api/generate` endpoint, which will handle the user\'s chapter continuation requests, and using `gemini-3.5-flash`.\n\n\n**Refining Narrative Style**\n\nI\'m now refining the narrative style to match \"\345\207\241\344\272\272\346\265\201.\" I\'m emphasizing Han Li\'s cautious nature, even in moments of vulnerability, contrasting with Song Yu\'s boldness and control. I am also working to ensure vivid descriptions of physical sensations and the interplay of spiritual energies, while maintaining the blend of eroticism and xianxia aesthetics.\n\n\n**Reviewing Server Structure**\n\nI\'m now reviewing the structure of the server. I\'m taking a close look at the \"Full-Stack Applications (Express + Vite)\" template to ensure that Vite and Express are correctly handled. I am confirming proper API route placement and the correct configuration of Vite middleware for both development and production.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create the backend entry point file `/server.ts` to implement the server-side proxy for the Gemini API (`gemini-3.5-flash`), allowing us to securely generate novel chapters using our private API key while maintaining compatibility with both development and production build states."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 14
      nanos: 813332802
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
