    thinking: "**Designing the UI**\n\nOkay, I\'m shifting gears now. The UI design in `src/App.tsx` takes center stage. But before diving in, I need to craft the perfect continuation of Part 5. Let\'s revisit the user\'s last input for inspiration. It\'s time to create that content.\n\n\n**Crafting the New Chapter**\n\nI\'m now deep in the writing of Chapter 6, aiming for that immersive continuation. I\'m focusing on \"\347\201\265\345\212\233\345\205\261\351\270\243\357\274\214\345\217\214\344\277\256\347\232\204\344\275\231\346\270\251\344\270\216\345\245\221\347\272\246,\" as the chapter title suggests. The goal is 1000 Chinese characters detailing the aftermath, the secret transaction, and the physical connection\'s essence. I\'ve re-examined the preloaded chapters to ensure cohesion within the React app. The list is set, so Chapter 6 is on its way.\n\n\n**Analyzing the Aftermath**\n\nI\'m now analyzing the aftermath of their encounter. The loss of Yuan Yang feels significant, weakening my power and leaving me physically drained, with persistent sensations. The younger woman, seemingly energized and advanced, has gained substantially, pushing towards the late Golden Core stage, an advancement that stings given the circumstances.\n\n\n**Considering the Power Dynamics**\n\nI\'m now contemplating the power dynamics. Specifically, I am analyzing Song Yu\'s actions and words, particularly her provocative touch and the veiled threats about the \"Chui Cha Immortal,\" and her mention of Nan Gong. The aim is to understand her strategy, and the leverage she holds over me, as I am physically weakened and mentally considering the ramifications. The interplay between her actions and implied threats is paramount, and is the key to my current strategic assessment.\n\n\n**Assessing the Agreement**\n\nI\'m now grappling with Song Yu\'s proposition. My body stiffened, and any murderous intent dissipated into a weary sigh; retribution is not worth further problems. The demand is a monthly meeting, with my mentoring as the facade, and her leveraging the \"Tongming Lingxi.\" Her touch is distracting and I am physically vulnerable. If I refuse, a compromising item will surface. My breaths are uneven as the situation intensifies.\n\n\n**Planning the Next Steps**\n\nNow, I\'m pivoting to the practical implementation within our single-page application. I\'m focusing on crafting a fantastic \"\345\260\217\350\257\264\351\230\205\350\257\273\345\231\250\" (novel reader) with high-quality styling. The core will be a selection menu for the first six chapters, and some basic reading settings. The first choices are for background (themes): Dark Ambient Slate/Gold, Minimal Soft Silver/Indigo, and Bamboo Forest, with the goal of creating a responsive and engaging user experience.\n\n\n**Developing the Feature Suite**\n\nI\'m now implementing the UI elements for the novel reader. I\'m focusing on features such as font pairing, adjustable font sizes, and an auto-scroll control with adjustable speed for ease of use. I\'m also excited to incorporate a custom ambient sound feature using the Web Audio API, which will create a relaxing atmosphere with sounds like bamboo forest wind and mountain rain. Finally, I\'m working on the chapter continuation and AI generation options, enabling users to either read existing content or provide plot prompts for fresh, AI-generated chapters from Gemini.\n\n\n"
